cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.DS, cs.LG. 

The paper deals with image processing and computer vision techniques for document image binarization. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves color space transformations and data analysis, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.MM (Multimedia). Additionally, the paper uses statistical methods to balance the amount of information on all color channels, which could be categorized under cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
